                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 337.11/260</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Gonzales</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-03-12T11:00:00-05:29">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 12, 1917, 11 a.m</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Last midnight succeeded in getting body fifty regulars to start from Nuevitas to
                    La Gloria for the protection of isolated and apprehensive American colony.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
